snippet: The case of a Sheboygan woman accused of killing her baby in 1957 is heading to trial after an attempt at a plea agreement fell through on Tuesday.
abstract: Case of Ruby Klokow, Sheboygan, Wis, woman accused of killing her baby in 1957, is heading to trial after an attempt at a plea agreement falls through.
lead_paragraph: The case of a Sheboygan woman accused of killing her baby in 1957 is heading to trial after an attempt at a plea agreement fell through on Tuesday.
